Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來中杉小夜香被硫加寄生的事實是錯不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通過你得到的樣本的分析結果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確認了硫加的存在資料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麥基烏斯警官  真的沒有拯救宿主的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  你的心情可以理解  但恐怕已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祗官到達地球就會馬上開始對硫加的處理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.27,0:00:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們一旦開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不會在乎給地球造成多大傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你在乎地球的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.98,0:00:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  到太空船上來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來得正好  有件事必須告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警官！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功君  你身體的修復工作完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？太好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  巴迪  你不高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然高興了  太好了  功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好啦  自由真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嘛  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  我說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易我們都恢復到原來的身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼沒什麼精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  其實  硫加…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學就是硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人  騙人啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我不管什麼事情都能以豁達的胸襟接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新學期剛開始就一副鬆懈的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀  是早宮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  約會進展怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不至於襲擊了中杉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你別瞎說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉來了我可得問問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你慌什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…早宮！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是中杉同學的爺爺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs20\fad(0,1200)}中杉IT公司的會長被殺\N於家中工作的傭人鈴木良枝（64）\N因涉嫌殺人正在被追查之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  開學典禮馬上開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要早退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目前中杉家這邊如畫面所示已經進行了交通管制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現場陷於混亂的氣氛中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目前還沒有抓到犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們將關注警方今後的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  讓我過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  這裡不讓過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請問  中杉小夜香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  說你呢  不許進來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您撥打的電話可能不在服務區內或者正關機  暫時無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉的爺爺看著那麼慈祥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事件當天開始下落不明的中杉家的傭人作為重要嫌疑人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傭人指的是鈴木良枝？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧  中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有點不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼只是在中杉同學的身邊不斷發生奇怪的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是被捲進了什麼麻煩之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  其實呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天開始能暫時留在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保護中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果她遇到什麼危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  希望你能幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了  巴迪  事情就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:05:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和中杉同學聯絡上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能  她家裡的電話也沒人接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情況還很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媒體也有很多人在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川君今天真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是個懶蟲  不用管他就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經第三天了  到極限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  再待一會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  硫加那方面沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…調查還很費勁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  但要是知道了什麼消息就跟我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我幫不上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不快點找到硫加就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  巴迪也沒精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  抓到硫加了怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,處理…啊  就是殺掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  被硫加寄生的人會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會一起死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉勝利遇害事件的調查情況沒有什麼進展
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉工業技術公司正在舉行葬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏瑪朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功…功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你滿意了吧  到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  再等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在和中杉取得聯絡前我想就這樣守望著她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  功  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必須和你說點事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別嚇一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實硫加的事情已經查清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加就寄生在中杉同學身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要把中杉同學給…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功？唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  關鍵時刻你竟然睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  要趕緊回到中杉同學那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後捕獲她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要說的話不是「捕獲」而是「保護」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保護
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆把她藏家裡來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉小姐被硫加寄生了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加在她體內成長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她自身正逐漸變成硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要捕獲她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別開這麼無聊的玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這讓我怎麼相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有證據嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她的汗水成分中查到了硫加的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她的汗水是什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你利用了我是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  但硫加對地球來說太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去全人類都會滅亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要殺掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要把中杉同學殺掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不把硫加處理掉會死很多人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是中杉同學…中杉同學她又沒做錯什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼  為什麼一定要殺她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,理解一下  功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了拯救眾多的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是弄錯了  說她是硫加一定是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身體怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕不讓你到中杉同學那兒去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川功封住了巴迪的意識  控制了身體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經出現精神融合的徵兆了  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才真是危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麥基烏斯警官
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈丘拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我要求她全面協助神祗廳  可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  按她說的做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有保護千川功生活的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒那個必要了  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？咦？咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們應該通知了你會把他的身體帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不能擅自就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒時間爭論這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要馬上捕獲硫加並處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服  衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眼鏡  眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀  偏偏這時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了  請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是從這裡消失的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能估計到她會去哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起到處瞎找不如在這等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你不願捕獲硫加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祗廳真的不知道解救被硫加寄生的宿主的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾  沒那樣的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我想說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是聯邦搜查官嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好像還有個其他的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能還是快點控制住硫加比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對方會自己送上門來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的做法不會有失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  突然來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手機放在親戚的婆婆那裡了  沒法和你聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給你添麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有的事  中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很不安  很孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺竟然去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連良枝阿姨都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…放哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  看到千川同學的臉就松了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直有很多人在家裡進出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不太友善的那種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  大家都很親切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都是剛見面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很親切  親切到讓人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功嗎  中杉同學跟你在一塊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  她不在我這
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想強行帶她走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把中杉同學交給我  功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加要被處理掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學已經和硫加同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加顯現出來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上又會重複比爾蓋巴的慘劇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人類會全部滅亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她才不是硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來說服失敗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈丘拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祗廳對硫加的處理延期了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聯邦政府內部在對硫加的處理一事上產生了爭議
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有人想拿地球來做硫加的試驗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「失落技術」的試驗場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,低度文明的當地人死多少都無所謂的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們逃跑吧  中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜歡現在聚在你身邊的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能去他們那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我遠走高飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,離這裡遠遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學  來  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有點逃亡者的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃到哪裡去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去北方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是去南方？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的盡頭怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒帶護照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:17:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說認真的啊  千川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:17:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊搶銀行  一邊亡命天涯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用擔心錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就來練習下逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快  跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就像「雌雄大盜」那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(369,363)\fs23}Bonnie and Clyde
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的一部電影  講的是一對戀人一邊搶銀行一邊旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…那兩人最後怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被警官開槍擊中  兩人都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川同學跟我一塊的話死也無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能立馬回答就沒希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒關係  我會當盾牌守護千川同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能那樣  我好歹也是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了保護中杉同學而死去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  千川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去薩塔吉特·夏瑪朗先生那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏瑪朗？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遠房親戚都只是想要爺爺的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺公司裡的也是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是夏瑪朗先生很尊重爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以很擔心公司和我
